title: Beautiful Breakfast Tortillas | Jamie Oliver
description:
Jamie's making some amazing Breakfast Tortillas, inspired by his time in East LA. This recipe is a perfect breakfast, brunch or lunch, packed full of Mexican inspired flavour. Silky eggs, avocado, delicious fresh tomatoes, manchego cheese and Jamie's homemade chilli sauce - what's not to love? Give it a go guys.
